      <section eId="sec_CC-749">
        <num>CC 749</num>
        <heading>749.  Extent and manner of use of servitude when title is silent</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 749.  Extent and manner of use of servitude when title is silent.
If the title is silent as to the extent and manner of use of the servitude, the intention of the parties is to be determined in the light of its purpose.</p>
        </content>
